data.description: New to the market Showcasing Florida's finest! This elegantly decorated and designed Pool home exceptionally blends the art of indoor and outdoor living. Vast Sliders open to the outdoor space equipped with ample sitting and dining areas overlooking the well-manicured backyard and pool with water feature in an oversized screened pool cage and lanai. the home's floor plan has been expanded to add extra living area, a Den/Library 1/2 bath extended laundry room, and an inside storage closet for additional home storage. The master bedroom has pool access and is quite large with 2 walking closets and an oversized master bath. As you look through the photos, notice the custom window treatments and the tasteful choice of warm and cool colors sharing the designer's touch. Schedule your personal tour. Home is equipped with solar panels for a true saving on electric charges Be sure to contact your agent for additional details today.
